<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>성인인증 완료</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .header {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    
    .user-info {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    
    .user-icon {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .user-details h3 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
    
    .user-details p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    
    .header-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .btn-logout {
      background: #ff4757;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .btn-logout:hover {
      background: #ff3838;
    }
    
    .content {
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .welcome-msg {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .success-icon {
      font-size: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .info-message {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    
    .feature-card {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .feature-title {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    
    .feature-desc {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .demo-content {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    
    .demo-title {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .demo-text {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .demo-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .demo-btn {
      background: #667eea;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .demo-btn:hover {
      background: #5a6fd8;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .header {
        padding: 15px;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .welcome-msg {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      
      .success-icon {
        font-size: 60px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="user-info">
      <div class="user-icon">
        <%= userInfo.name ? userInfo.name.charAt(0) : 'U' %>
      </div>
      <div class="user-details">
        <h3><%= userInfo.name || '사용자' %>님</h3>
        <p>성인인증 완료 ✓</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-buttons">
      <a href="/logout" class="btn-logout">로그아웃</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
    <h1 class="welcome-msg">성인인증이 완료되었습니다!</h1>
    <p class="info-message">
      이제 모든 서비스를 자유롭게 이용하실 수 있습니다.<br>
      안전하고 즐거운 이용 되시기 바랍니다.
    </p>
    
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
        <div class="feature-title">안전한 서비스</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">인증된 성인 사용자만 접근 가능</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
        <div class="feature-title">개인정보 보호</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">최소한의 정보만 수집</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="feature-title">빠른 인증</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">간편한 휴대폰 본인인증</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
        <div class="feature-title">모바일 지원</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">모든 기기에서 이용 가능</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 여기에 실제 서비스 콘텐츠를 추가하세요 -->
    <div class="demo-content">
      <h2 class="demo-title">🎉 환영합니다!</h2>
      <p class="demo-text">
        성인인증이 완료되어 이제 모든 콘텐츠에 접근하실 수 있습니다.<br>
        아래는 데모 버튼들입니다. 실제 서비스에 맞게 수정해주세요.
      </p>
      <div class="demo-buttons">
        <button class="demo-btn" onclick="alert('데모 기능 1')">기능 1</button>
        <button class="demo-btn" onclick="alert('데모 기능 2')">기능 2</button>
        <button class="demo-btn" onclick="alert('데모 기능 3')">기능 3</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    // 여기에 실제 서비스 JavaScript 코드를 추가하세요
    console.log('성인인증 완료: 사용자 =', '<%= userInfo.name || "사용자" %>');
    
    // 예시: 페이지 로드 시 환영 메시지
    window.addEventListener('load', function() {
      setTimeout(() => {
        console.log('메인 페이지가 로드되었습니다.');
      }, 1000);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>